      • QR

        public QR(String message,
          String path,
          String filename)
        Constructor with 3 simple parameter to produce a QR
        Parameters:
        message - the message to encode into QR code
        path - the path where the QR code image to be placed
        filename - the name of the QR code file to be generated

        Example:

        QR qr = new QR("foo bar","/path/to/image","foobar");
